\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Dumal Lunnash had been a historian and one of the men to have survived Jere Harash\'92s last attempt to master the spirit world completely. Upon the young man\'92s attaining the trance state necessary to transfer the energy to the spells he wove, a spirit had taken control of his body and gone on a killing rampage. Later, the Vizjerei had learned that the spirits they called on and unwittingly unleashed into the world were demons from the Burning Hells.
