\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93Then I\'92m surprised that you came at all,\'94 Cholik said. This was a conversation they\'92d been avoiding for months, and he was surprised to find it coming out now. But only in a way. From the signs they\'92d been finding the last week, while Raithen had been away plundering and pillaging, or whatever it was that Raithen\'92s pirates did while they were away, Cholik had known they were close to discovering the dead city\'92s most important secret.
