\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Turning from the bigger man, Cholik paced on the balcony in an effort to warm himself against the night\'92s chill.\plain \f2\i\fs24 I{\*\bkmkstart RichViewCheckpoint11}{\*\bkmkend RichViewCheckpoint11}knew it would come to this at some point,\plain \f2\fs24 he told himself.\plain \f2\i\fs24 This was to be expected.\plain \f2\fs24 He let out a long, deliberate breath, letting Raithen think for a time that he\'92d gotten the better of him. Over his years as a priest, Cholik had found that men often made even more egregious mistakes when they\'92d been praised for their intelligence or their power.
