\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Only a few moments later, after branching off into the newest group of tunnels that had been made through Ransim\'92s remains, Cholik spotted the intense glare created by the torches and campfires the excavation team had established. The team had divided into shifts, breaking into groups. Each group toiled sixteen hours, with an eight-hour overlap scheduled for clearing out the debris that had been dug out of the latest access tunnels. They slept eight hours a day because Cholik found that they couldn\'92t be worked any more than sixteen hours without some rest and sleep and still stay healthy for any appreciable length of time.
