\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Raithen grinned. \'93Damn me for a fool, but you do me well, wench. Spoken like you\'92d looked deep inside my own heart.\'94 He gazed down at her. \'93See? Now, most people would think you were only talking. Running your mouth to play yourself up, to make yourself feel maybe a little braver. But I look into your eyes, and I know you\'92re speaking the truth.\'94
