\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Raithen prepared for the worst, spinning and placing{\*\bkmkstart RichViewCheckpoint45}{\*\bkmkend RichViewCheckpoint45}the corpse between himself and the doorway. He slipped the knife free of the dead woman\'92s flesh and held it before him.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  A grizzled man stepped into the room with a crossbow in his hands. He squinted against the bright light streaming from the fireplace. \'93Cap\'92n? Cap\'92n Raithen?\'94 The crossbow held steady in the man\'92s hands, aimed at the two bodies.
