\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  The sailor pulled the crossbow off line and canted the metal-encased butt against his hip. He reached up and doffed his tricorn hat. \'93Begging the cap\'92s pardon, but I thought ye was in some fair amount of rough water there. With all that squallering a-goin\'92 on, I mean. Didn\'92t know you was up here after enjoying yerself with one of the doxies.\'94
