\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Pettit grinned and spat into the dented bronze cuspidor in the corner of the room. He wiped his mouth with the back of his hand, then said, \'93Looks like ye\'92ve about had yer fill of that one. Want me to bring another one up?\'94
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93No.\'94 Controlling the fear and curiosity that raged within him, Raithen cleaned his bloody knife on the woman\'92s clothes, then crossed the room to the mirror. It was cracked and contained dark gray age spots where the silver-powder backing had worn away. \'93But she did remind me of something, Pettit.\'94
