\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  The man remained silent.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93I\'92ll not trouble myself to ask you again,\'94 Darrick warned. \'93At this point, and take care to fully understand what I\'92m telling you here, you\'92re a better bargain to me dead than you are alive. I don\'92t look forward to trying to complete the rest of my mission while bringing along a prisoner.\'94
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Lon swallowed and tried to look defiant.
