\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Lying on the ground as he was, Darrick knew it was hard for the pirate to feel in any way in control of the situation.{\*\bkmkstart RichViewCheckpoint51}{\*\bkmkend RichViewCheckpoint51}And Mat\'92s words made sense. The pirate just didn\'92t know Mat wouldn\'92t let Darrick act on an impulse like that. Anyway, the loss of control was behind him, and Darrick was in command of himself again.
