\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93Well,\'94 Mat admitted, \'93it was a sound plan on your part. I\'92d probably have tried the same thing. But we\'92re here on some matter of consequence, ye see.\'94
