\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93What about the king\'92s nephew?\'94 Mat asked. \'93He\'92s just a boy, an\'92 I wouldn\'92t want to hear that anything untoward has happened to him.\'94
