\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Leaning, Pettit spat again, missing the cuspidor this time. He rubbed strings of spittle from his chin. \'93That there\'92s a symbol what Valdir saw on that door. It\'92s a huge door, cap\'92n, near to three times as tall as a man, the way Valdir puts it.\'94
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93You spoke to him?\'94
