\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  One of the mercenaries stepped forward and cut the ragged shirt from a slave with quick flicks of his dagger. He dipped the shirt into another bucket of water, then{\*\bkmkstart RichViewCheckpoint61}{\*\bkmkend RichViewCheckpoint61}plopped the soaked garment on top of the fire. Sizzling, the fire died.
