\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Cholik continued speaking, feeling stronger as the spell bound the man to him. His words came faster and more certain. The invisible hands spread-eagled the slave on the ground, then lifted him up, dangling him in the air.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93No!\'94 the man screamed. \'93Please! I beg you! I will work! I will work!\'94
