\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Once, the man\'92s fear and his pleading might have{\*\bkmkstart RichViewCheckpoint62}{\*\bkmkend RichViewCheckpoint62}touched Cholik. Those things did not touch Cholik intimately, for the old priest could never remember a time when he\'92d placed the needs of another above his own. But there had been times he\'92d gone with the Zakarum Church missionaries in the past to heal the sick and tend to wounded men. The recent trouble between Westmarch and Tristram had been rife with those incidents.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93Nooooo!\'94 the man screamed.
