\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Darrick started down the grade, staying along the edge of the river. The block-and-tackles and the guards were nearly two hundred yards away. Brush and small trees grew along the high riverbank. Raithen\'92s pirates had been lazy about clearing more land than necessary.
