\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93Once we give the signal,\'94 Darrick said, \'93bring the rest of the men in a hurry. We\'92ll be boarding the middle ship to look for the king\'92s nephew. When we find him, I\'92ll be having him off that ship soon as we\'92re able. Make use of one of those block-and-tackles. Understand?\'94
