\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Pressing himself against the mountainside, Raithen{\*\bkmkstart RichViewCheckpoint73}{\*\bkmkend RichViewCheckpoint73}watched as a short, squat barrel was let go. The pulleys slowed the barrel\'92s descent, proving that the load was light. The scent of salted pork passed within inches of Raithen.
