\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93Evenin\'92, cap\'92n,\'94 a scar-faced pirate greeted. A half dozen other pirates did the same but didn\'92t slow in their efforts to take the food from the barrel.
