\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Planks spanned the distance between the ships. The river current was gentle enough that the cogs didn\'92t fight the tether while they lay at anchorage. On board\plain \f2\i\fs24 Barracuda,\plain \f2\fs24 the ship kept between the other two, he saw Bull sitting in the prow puffing on a pipe.
