\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93Cap\'92n,\'94 Bull acknowledged, taking the pipe from between his teeth. He was a big man, seemingly assembled from masts. A scarf tied around his head bound his{\*\bkmkstart RichViewCheckpoint74}{\*\bkmkend RichViewCheckpoint74}wounded ear, but bloodstains were visible down the sides of his neck.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93How\'92s the boy, Bull?\'94 Raithen asked.
