\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93Why, he\'92s fine, cap\'92n,\'94 Bull replied. \'93Any reason he shouldn\'92t be?\'94
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
