\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93I\'92m not worrying over it,\'94 Raithen said. \'93I figure any pirate who gets taken in by a boy isn\'92t worth the salt I pay him to crew my ship.\'94
