\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Bull\'92s face darkened, but Raithen knew it was out of embarrassment. \'93It\'92s just that he\'92s such an innocent-lookin\'92 thing, cap\'92n. Didn\'92t figure him for no shenanigans like this. An\'92 that two-by-four? Why, he like to took me plumb by surprise. I\'92m right tempted to keep him fer myself if\'92n the king don\'92t ransom him back. I\'92m tellin\'92 ye true, cap\'92n, we\'92ve done a lot worse than take on somebody like this boy for crew.\'94
