\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93Aye, sir.\'94 Bull took a massive key ring from his waist sash, then knocked the contents of his pipe into the river. No fires except the watch\'92s lanterns were allowed down in the hold, and those were taken there seldom.
