\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Lhex swallowed again. \'93Yes.\'94
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93Good.\'94 Raithen raised the lantern, getting it out of the boy\'92s eyes and letting him see the smile on his face. \'93This doesn\'92t have to go hard for you, boy. But I mean to have the information I came here for tonight.\'94
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
