\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93I can handle a small boy,\'94 Raithen said, hanging the lantern on a hook on the wall. He took the key from Bull and sent the pirate on his way with a look. Gripping the bars of the door with one hand, Raithen closed the door. The clang of metal on metal sounded loud in the enclosed space.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 {\*\bkmkstart RichViewCheckpoint77}{\*\bkmkend RichViewCheckpoint77}
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Lhex started to get to his feet.
