\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  There was no stopping it now, though. Darrick beat back the big mercenary\'92s defenses, chasing the man steadily backward. Syrnon called out for help, but even the other mercenaries appeared loath to step into the fray.
