\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Part of Darrick knew the whistle signaled the arrival of the king\'92s Peacekeepers. All of the Peacekeepers were tough men and women dedicated to keeping the king\'92s peace inside the city walls.
