\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Darrick closed his good eye. The other was swollen shut and filled with blood. The sailor he\'92d fought in Gargan\'92s Greased Eel had fought with an enchanted weapon and snapped into action quicker than Darrick had thought.
