\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  The man was tall and big, but that was somewhat hidden beneath the simple woolen traveling cloak he wore. His clothing was old and patched, showing signs of hard usage and covered over with road dust and grit. The frayed kerchief at his neck was tied by a sailor\'92s knot that Uncle Ramais had showed her. The man stood like a shadow carved out of the crowd.
