\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93You must be,\'94 Taramis said. \'93I can think of no other. Your friend died in that place. There has to be a reason you were spared. It\'92s the balance, Darrick. The needs of the Light must always be balanced against the power of the Darkness.\'94
