\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Pushing away his own fears, going numb and dead inside the way he had when he\'92d faced his father in that{\*\bkmkstart RichViewCheckpoint274}{\*\bkmkend RichViewCheckpoint274}small barn in Hillsfar, Darrick stepped toward the dead man. He reached for the sword.
