\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Darrick strained for the sword, wanting even another fraction of an inch if he could get it. It felt as if his finger bones were going to pass through the flesh. Pain raced up his arm, and he clenched his teeth against it.
