\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Pain dimmed Darrick\'92s hearing. Images of Mat falling from the cliffside spun through his brain again. Guilt filled Darrick, echoed by the worthlessness he felt from his father\'92s oft-repeated words. For a moment, he thought the pain was going to destroy him, melt him down where he{\*\bkmkstart RichViewCheckpoint275}{\*\bkmkend RichViewCheckpoint275}stood. He was locked in the pursuit of the sword, didn\'92t think he could pull back if he wanted to.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  And where would he go from here after failing this? He had no answers.
