\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93Mat?\'94 Darrick said aloud. He was so surprised at hearing Mat\'92s voice that he didn\'92t even realize at first that he had fallen across the corpse, bruising his knees against the earthen floor. Instinctively, his hand curled around the sword\'92s hilt, but he glanced around the shadows of the crypt looking for Mat Hu-Ring.
