\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  The old man tried to touch the weapon as well but with the same results. \'93Nor can I. None in my family has ever been able to touch the sword. Whenever we moved it, we had to move Hauklin\'92s body as well.\'94 A note of sadness sounded in the old man\'92s voice.
