\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  For the first time, Darrick realized that taking the sword would leave the old man and his grandson with nothing to care for or protect. Darrick gazed at the old man. \'93I\'92m sorry,\'94 he whispered.
