\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Ellig Barrows nodded. \'93All of us who have defended the sword have prayed that this day would come, this day when we would be free of our burden, but to see it actually happen\'97\'94 Words failed him.
