\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93Taramis!\'94 one of the men shouted from outside.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Even as the sage started for the magical door, the sound of inhuman and monstrous yips and growls cascaded into the root cellar.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Darrick followed the sage, bolting through the racks of foodstuffs and wines, trailed by Ellig Barrows with the lantern. The weak gray daylight pouring through the root cellar door marked the entrance.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  The noise of men fighting, their curses and yells, as well as the growls and howls of the creatures they fought, pummeled Darrick\'92s ears as he raced up the earthen steps. He was on Taramis\'92s heels as they burst from the root cellar.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  The clearing around the house, which had moments ago been peaceful and restful, was now filled with battle. Taramis\'92s warriors formed a quick skirmish line against the bloodthirsty beasts that raged against them from the forest.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93Lezanti,\'94 Taramis breathed. \'93By the Light, Kabraxis has found us out.\'94
