\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Darrick slid the sword under the trapdoor\'92s edge and levered it up, revealing the ladder beneath.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  The boy took a lantern from the floor and reached for the old woman. \'93Come on, Grandmother.\'94
