\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Darrick heard the missiles whistle by his head within inches of striking him. He pulled himself behind the center mast, trusting the magical winds that Taramis had stirred up to drive\plain \f2\i\fs24 Blue Zephyr\plain \f2\fs24 into the pilings. Overhead, more quarrels ripped through the canvas sails.
