\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Looking over the stern railing, Darrick saw a guard ship streaking for them. Lanterns lighted Lord Darkulan\'92s flag in the stern and on the prow, marking the vessel for all to see.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93The torch is too weak,\'94 Taramis said. \'93But it\'92s got to be down there.\'94 He waved the torch, reaching down as far as he could, but it was futile. The light simply wouldn\'92t reach the riverbank properly.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
