\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Turning, knowing he wasn\'92t going to find his friend standing somewhere behind him the way it sounded, Darrick looked at the warriors assembling in the stern, looking toward Taramis to call their next move.
