\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f2\i\fs24  The sword, ye damned fool!\plain \f2\fs24 Mat said.\plain \f2\i\fs24 Draw the bloody great sword. It\'92ll help ye an\'92 them with ye.
