\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Taramis and the other warriors holding lanterns and torches they\'92d gotten from the whale-oil freighter tried to penetrate the shadows covering the riverbank.
