\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93Mat,\'94 Darrick whispered, hurting inside as if he\'92d just witnessed his friend\'92s death. He wasn\'92t imagining Mat\'92s voice. It was real. It was real, and it was inside his head.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f2\i\fs24  Call out the sword\'92s name, ye great lumberin\'92 lummox,\plain \f2\fs24 Mat ordered.
