\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  The sour smell of the hay in the stable behind his father\'92s butcher shop swirled around Darrick. He could almost feel the heat of the day press against him, trapped by the small crawlspace among the rafters where the hay was kept. And where he\'92d lain while waiting to die or be killed the next time his father beat him.
