\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  The guards erupted from the checkpoint, and the demon{\*\bkmkstart RichViewCheckpoint341}{\*\bkmkend RichViewCheckpoint341}hunters ran to meet them. Steel rang on steel, and Darrick was in the thick of them.
