\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Darrick battled for his life. Outnumbered as they were at the moment, he knew it was only going to get worse. He parried and riposted, turning a blade aside, then following through behind the point as it sank through the heart of a mercenary. Placing his foot against the dead man\'92s chest, Darrick kicked him backward into three others who rushed to take his spot.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
