\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  But even though Darrick had dealt with the one opponent,{\*\bkmkstart RichViewCheckpoint342}{\*\bkmkend RichViewCheckpoint342}others stepped up immediately to take his place. And the man Darrick had engaged had slipped his weapon free. The guard slashed at Darrick\'92s face as the dark cloud overhead roiled and flashed. Darrick trapped the man\'92s blade again, set himself, twisted, and drove a foot into the man\'92s head, knocking him from his feet and back into a knot of worshippers.
