\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Darrick blocked, blocked again, parried, and riposted, putting his point through a man\'92s throat. Scarlet bubbled at the guard\'92s throat as he stumbled backward, dropped his sword, and wrapped both hands around his neck in an effort to stem the blood flow.
