\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Unable to change directions in the air, Darrick fell, dropping like a stone into the waiting snake\'92s mouth. Flames wrapped him, and for an instant he thought he was going to be incinerated. Unbelievable heat surrounded him and stole his senses away.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f2\i\fs24  Stand easy,\plain \f2\fs24 Mat warned. His voice, even though Darrick was certain it came from within his head, also sounded distant and small.\plain \f2\i\fs24 This is going to be the worst of it, Darrick, an\'92 there ain\'92t no way around it.
