\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Darrick couldn\'92t believe he wasn\'92t dead. The fall alone against the stone mouth of the snake should have killed him, but the addition of the flames had taken away all chance of his survival.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Yet\'97
