\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Darrick recognized the voice as his father\'92s. His eyes snapped open, and he saw the familiar stable area behind his father\'92s butcher shop. He found himself lying on the sour hay that lined the hayloft.
