\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93Get up, I said,\'94 his father roared. He was a big man with a broad belly and shoulders as wide as an ax handle. His hands were big and tough from hard work and long hours and countless tavern fights. A curly mop of brown hair matched the curly beard he wore to mid-chest.
