\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Face burning in shame, Darrick looked down at himself. He was a boy, no more than eight or nine. No threat at all to his father. Yet his father treated him like the fiercest opponent he\'92d ever encountered.
