\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Darrick took the blow on the back of his head, watched the world spin around him for a moment, and remembered how only last week he\'92d watched his father beat three caravan guards in a fight in the muddy street outside the Lame Goose Tavern. As a butcher, his father was passable, but as a fighter, there were few who could compare.
