\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  But how could he know what that felt like? Other than{\*\bkmkstart RichViewCheckpoint348}{\*\bkmkend RichViewCheckpoint348}one of the stories he sometimes overheard outside the taverns his father frequented in the evening. His father always tried to leave Darrick at home, but his mother was seldom there in the evenings, and Darrick had been too afraid to sit at home alone.
