\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Darrick breathed shallowly, certain he\'92d heard Mat Hu-Ring\'92s voice. But that couldn\'92t be, could it? Mat was dead. He\'92d died . . . died . . .
