\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  His father cinched the hangman\'92s knot tight under the corner of his jaw. \'93Time to go,\'94 his father growled. \'93At least when this story goes through the town, they\'92ll say my son went out with the courage of his da.\'94
