\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  Through dying vision growing black around the edges, Darrick saw his father\'92s shadow on the wall behind him. Only it wasn\'92t his father\'92s. Whatever cast the shadow on the wall there wasn\'92t human. Then Darrick remembered the cathedral in Bramwell, the stone serpent with the flaming maw.
