\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  \'93You\'92re too late,\'94 the demon said. His form changed, shifting from that of Darrick\'92s father to his own true nature. \'93You\'92re going to die here, and I\'92m going to have your soul. Perhaps you\'92ve killed Buyard Cholik, but I\'92ll use you to anchor me to this world.\'94
