\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  With the noose still around his neck, restricting his airways and causing spots before his eyes, Darrick fought. The sword was a live thing in his hands, moving inhumanly quick, but it was only enough to keep his inhuman opponent from killing him.
