\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0  When he opened his eyes again, he stood in the center of the cathedral. Snow covered the floor around him. He had Kabraxis\'92s head in his hand, gripping it by one of the horns.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 {\*\bkmkstart RichViewCheckpoint352}{\*\bkmkend RichViewCheckpoint352}
